      ]
    },
    {
      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Control is not the same as doing it yourself",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">A good delegation system increases trust because everyone knows where autonomy starts and where support appears.</p>"
        },
